Ye sab **social engineering attacks** hain, jisme attackers psychological tricks use karke logon se sensitive information nikalne ki koshish karte hain. Samjhne ke liye ek-ek point ko breakdown karte hain:  

### 1ï¸âƒ£ **Phishing**  
Attackers **fake emails, messages, ya websites** ka use karte hain taaki log apna **username, password, ya financial details** unhe de dein.  
ğŸ›¡ **Bachav ka tarika:**  
âœ… **Email me URL check karein**, agar kuch alag lage (spelling mistake, extra characters, ya unknown sender) to uspe click mat karein.  
âœ… **Fake login pages se bachein** â€“ hamesha manually website ka URL type karein.  

### 2ï¸âƒ£ **Shoulder Surfing**  
Ye tab hota hai jab **koi aapka screen ya keyboard ka data dekh raha hota hai** bina aapke permission ke. Public places me zyada hota hai.  
ğŸ›¡ **Bachav ka tarika:**  
âœ… **Privacy screen filters** use karein.  
âœ… **Apni screen aur passwords ko cover karein jab enter kar rahe ho.**  

### 3ï¸âƒ£ **Tailgating & Piggybacking**  
Ye **physical security breach** hai, jisme ek **unauthorized person bina permission ke kisi authorized person ke saath enter kar jata hai.**  
ğŸ›¡ **Bachav ka tarika:**  
âœ… **Access cards ya biometric security enforce karein.**  
âœ… **Strangers ko bina verification ke andar na aane dein.**  

### 4ï¸âƒ£ **Dumpster Diving**  
Attackers **trash bins ya dustbins me documents, receipts, ya hard drives dhundh kar sensitive information nikal sakte hain.**  
ğŸ›¡ **Bachav ka tarika:**  
âœ… **Har sensitive document ko shred karein.**  
âœ… **Digital data securely delete karein (wiping software use karein).**  

